			<h1><img src="/content/work/4.cloudee/i/logo.png" alt="Cloudee" width="265" height="58"></h1>
			<p>I was contacted by the guys at Boxee to help produce a series of mobile-focused HTML email templates for Cloudee, a new video-sharing service made for the iPhone.</p>
			<div class="idid">
				<small>My Role</small>
				<ul>
					<li class="email">HTML Email</li>
				</ul>
			</div>
