	</div>
</div>
<div class="outside">
	<article class="inside">
		<section class="cf imgl nobottom">
			<div class="text">
				<h2>Mobile First Emails</h2>
				<p>I worked with Cloudee's talented creative team to bring their designs to life.</p>
				<p>Where necessary, we worked together to adjust each design based on <a href="http://www.campaignmonitor.com/css/" title="CSS Support in email clients" rel="external">CSS restrictions</a> of popular email clients.</p>
				<p>After the designs were finalized, I coded and tested each HTML template in several major email clients on both desktop and small screen. Since Cloudee is a mobile app, displaying the emails well on small screens was important. I wrote media queries to adapt the layout in iOS Mail (iPhone + iPad), Android, and mobile Gmail.</p>
				<img src="/i/emails.png" alt="email clients" height="55" width="350">
			</div>
			<figure><img src="/content/work/4.cloudee/i/cloudeeEmailSm.jpg" alt="Softwre Update Email" width="500" height="800"></figure>
		</section>
		<section class="cf full nobottom">
			<figure><img src="/content/work/4.cloudee/i/cloudee-series.jpg" alt="Cloudee series of emails" width="1000" height="500"></figure>
		</section>
	</article>
